制药商曾就此事进行了激烈的内部辩论和大力反击。戴琪表示，政府此举是为了尽快普及安全有效的疫苗，结束新冠疫情。她同时表示，美国政府将继续加强与私营部门和所有可能伙伴的合作，扩大疫苗的制造和分销，以及努力增加生产这些疫苗所需的原材料。 报道称，美国此举有可能扩大新冠疫苗的全球供应，缩小富国和穷国之间的疫苗接种差距。美国白宫办公厅主任罗恩·克莱因 2 日曾表示，知识产权是全球新冠肺炎疫苗短缺问题的一部分，但更大的问题在于制造业。他说，白宫将在「未来几天」透露更多消息。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-6ab4a07078a4006255755ad554d41fab_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "528 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/458001065"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4vWSuL7P47gbEAMaCDY0MDU4MDUxIOzjzIQGMBI42QJABXIJNDU4MDAxMDY1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1620268376.6704617", "card_id": "Q_321664580", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 405}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你在国外吃到过什么第一口就惊为天人的食物？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "都说国内国外饮食文化差异大，中国人在国外吃不惯，想知道外国有没有也很让你惊艳并且念念不忘的食物呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-c0b3d251a6e7df32c2cae9ec16ff6886_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "434 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/321664580"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4vWSuL7P47gbEAMaCDMzNzU3MDA3IPvRheYFMBA42TtABnIJMzIxNjY0NTgweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1620268376.670828", "card_id": "Q_39211784", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 4239}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "怎样在最短的篇幅内写出令人窒息的绝望感？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如何在最短字数内，写出令人感觉心脏被揪住的绝望感？ 相关问题：怎样在最短的篇幅内写出无可奈何的遗憾感？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-f01f35141f9a4a85c9fb57381c6ec195_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "398 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/39211784"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I4vWSuL7P47gbEAMaBzc4OTE5NjYg36+ytAUwNjjKwQFAB3IIMzkyMTE3ODR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=